  "title": "Temp Telesales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: The Central, Clarke Quay</strong></p><p><strong>Employment Type: Temporary</strong></p><p><strong>Hourly rates: SGD $10 – $12 per hour</strong></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Make outbound calls to contacts on a provided lead list.</li><li>Introduce company products/services and gather information from potential clients.</li><li>Identify qualified leads and escalate them to the sales team for follow-up.</li><li>Maintain accurate records of calls and outcomes in the CRM or provided system.</li><li>Support the sales team with general administrative tasks as needed.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Good communication skills in English (additional languages a plus).</li><li>Comfortable with making outbound calls and handling rejection.</li><li>Basic computer skills (MS Office, CRM systems).</li><li>Can work independently and follow instructions accurately.</li><li>Previous telesales or customer service experience preferred but not mandatory.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
